dc_title_s: To Her most Sacred Majesty Ann Queen of Great Britain, France & Ireland : this map of Europe according to the newest and most exact observations
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Inset: A new draught of ye artificiall channel ... made in order to passage of ships thro the rivers of Ilafla and Camisinca, and to the Wolga ...
dc_publisher_s: [London] : Printed for I. Bowles printseller at ye sign of ye Screen over against Stocks Market and T. Bowles print & mapseller next to the Chapter house in St. Pauls Church yard ; [London] : Sold by H. Moll over against Devereux Court, without Temple Bar and P. Overton map & printseller at ye Globe in the Poultry, 1708.
